narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Good, interesting class if you're interested in East Asia and films!
Very fun introduction to various East Asian contemporary cinemas, markets, traditions, etc.

I loved the movies that we watched in this course and thought it was a great way to get a taste for Asian cinema. I think given the make-up of the class (of mostly non-film studies majors) the class could have offered a more general introduction to film studies in the first week.
Take it if you really want to.learn about film.studies,.not films.
